xa0; </span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt">We offer the same </span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt">range of products to our customers and make lending decisions for both our individual customers </span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt">and business customers </span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt">in the same way. </span></p><p style="margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 27pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:-27pt"><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 27pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:-27pt"><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt; font-style:normal; font-weight:normal">1.3.</span><span style="font:7.0pt 'Times New Roman'">&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; </span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt">As a consequence of this, we do not believe that our customers are in any way disadvantaged by banking with </span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt">Santander</span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt"> in </span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt">Northern Ireland</span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt"> as opposed to those banking with us in </span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt">Great Britain</span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt">. </span></p><p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify"><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 27pt; text-align:justify"><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt; font-style:italic; font-weight:bold">Do banks </span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt; font-style:italic; font-weight:bold">that</span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt; font-style:italic; font-weight:bold"> operate in both GB and NI, </span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt; font-style:italic; font-weight:bold">eg</span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt; font-style:itali