aining branches in the area which we have, in turn, improved to accommodate all of our customers in the town.</span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt"> </span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt">This exercise has shown us that we are able to provide a better service to our cust</span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt">omers when we consol</span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt">idate all of our staff into one, larger </span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt">branch.</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify"><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 27pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:-27pt"><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt; font-style:normal; font-weight:normal">5.5.</span><span style="font:7.0pt 'Times New Roman'">&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; </span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt">Alongside our branch network, </span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt">Santander</span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt"> has an active “</span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt">omni</span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt">-channel” strategy to ensure that our customers can access our services in a variety of ways as suits their needs. This includes large domestic call </span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt">centres</span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt"> for phone inquiries, a comprehensive online banking platform and a mobile banki</span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt">ng app which was recently named best personal banking app in its category by mobile developer </span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt">Xtreme</span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt"> Labs.</span></p><p style="margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 9pt"><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt; font-style:italic">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="margin:0pt 